oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Billy Block's Western Beat American Music Showcase (Feb. 3)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Lackey, Jane, 1948-; Fasman, Barry; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (red on white) announcing Billy Block's Western Beat American Music Showcase featuring Vicki and Eddie Cunningham, Teresa James and Terry Wilson, Jodi Seigel and Danny Timms, Jane and Craig Lackey, Lisa and Barry Fasman, Judy Toy and Paul Inman, Tina and Alan Bolvin, Merrily Weeber and John Barnard, Jerry Willis and Alicia Carol, Molly Pasutti and Jamie Dunlap and special guest Julian Henslee at Highland Grounds on February 3. Poster features a metal photoplate of Billy Block's Western Beat logo.
